Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻过这座山之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 港口之都 哈里 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从 哈里 可以搭船到相邻的 拉克尔 大陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉克尔 那里有大型的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定可以找到能解读这本古文书的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有些什么重要的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那是在怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小兄弟 你是剑士吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也进去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是要干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才啊 有一位旅行的剑士为了消灭邪恶的魔物 到洞窟里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶的魔物？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每晚都出现在牧场 还把动物吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我养的牲畜全被吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他是剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个人进去太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们也进去帮他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 真是些强人所难的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办哪 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到有困难的人我们也不能不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是好心人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊… 看你们的啰…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是什么样的魔物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是能吃掉牛羊的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是非常巨大的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险 快出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把村子里的牧场一一捣毁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并把他们辛苦养大的家畜吃掉的邪恶魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 艾修顿•安卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替天行道 制裁你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种魔物我一个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 跌倒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾、蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～两位还真亲热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 龙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是怕了本艾修顿大爷 逃之夭夭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不中用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你、你们那是什么眼神啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…你背上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么会粘在我的背上！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快帮我拿下来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～谁来救我啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是你们害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛把责任都推到我们头上？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我全力保护你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果无法集中精神战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就没有保护到谁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 蕾娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎完全融合在一起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用蕾娜的治愈能力恢复不了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况的话就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴的纹章术能不能帮帮他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没听说过有那样的纹章术呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候玩捉迷藏每次都是我扮鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远足的当天一定会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一走在路上就会踩到屎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我总是背负这种厄运呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜它所赐总是碰到灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果都没人肯陪我一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～那么你是孤单一个人出来旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说孤单一个人～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢一个人旅行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样不是很好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来就有新同伴了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算哪门子的同伴哪～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以变成这样都是你们害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要负起责任吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办法倒是有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前看到过一本书上面是这么记载的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被龙附身者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以飞舞在天空的王者之泪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来净化其身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞舞在天空的王者之泪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有王者之泪者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被宁静的水面所环抱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹如母亲体内一般深邃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其降临的险峻山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受荣耀的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得胜利之时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝方可得到王者之泪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时咏诵誓词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随着强烈且痛苦的咆哮声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔龙将从世上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要得到飞舞在天空的王者之泪就行了 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被宁静的水面所环抱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹如母亲体内一般深邃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是位于克洛斯大陆西北方的\N克尔湖的山岳神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快点往那个神殿出发吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～龙龙它们在吃蛋糕耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了 可不可以给它们取名字啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别管这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只眼睛瞪得长长的就叫"长长"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只眼睛圆溜溜的就叫"圆圆"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们很喜欢耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个家伙袭击牧场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把家畜都吃光了耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个真的有袭击牧场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家都说不是了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别上当！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙这种动物是很凶恶的魔物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂～没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们等等我啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一觉得自己实在累得要死…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到这两个家伙还真重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只靠我一个人背着你们走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也给我下来走走行不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的废物…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊 精神不是超好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在刚才那个咖啡店买的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也给我一块
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长长和圆圆也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？我也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吃咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 你们俩要去哪儿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停、停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啦 很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我非找到王者之泪不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要特地跑来找魔物打架吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂～艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德 听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我跟魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么巨大的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按理说会有相当的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要循着波动寻找的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以找到他的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南南西的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感应到强大的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安无事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山脚下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长长 圆圆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…想不到我会变成这幅德行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太悲哀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…是不是丢下我继续旅行了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我非得被这种魔物附身不可呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并不是魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别用那种邪恶的称呼叫我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？谁…是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们在说话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 我听错了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是在这种地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 波动非常强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…我们已经离他们很近啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长长 圆圆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长长…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔物的巢穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫…子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德 你看那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了 袭击牧场的原来是这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌～虫子～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦 讨厌啦 讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我到前面去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想再走下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪哪 闪哪 闪哪 闪哪 闪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿 小心上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿！
